      'Dragon Age: Inquisition': 'A 2014 BioWare RPG set in the high-fantasy world of Thedas, featuring large open regions and party-based combat.',
      'The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt': 'A 2015 CD Projekt Red open-world RPG following Geralt of Rivia in a vast, morally complex fantasy world.',
      'Counter-Strike: Global Offensive': 'A competitive tactical first-person shooter by Valve, pitting terrorists against counter-terrorists.',
      'Overwatch': 'A 2016 Blizzard team-based hero shooter with colorful characters and objective-focused gameplay.',
      'Rez Infinite': 'A 2016 rail shooter by Enhance Games, blending music and visuals in a synesthetic on-rails experience.',
      'The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild': 'A 2017 Nintendo open-world adventure game where Link explores a vast Hyrule with emergent physics-based gameplay.',
      'Resident Evil 7: Biohazard': 'A 2017 Capcom survival horror game shifting to first-person perspective in a decaying Louisiana plantation.',
      'God of War': 'A 2018 Sony Santa Monica action-adventure following Kratos and his son Atreus through Norse mythology.',
      'Astro Bot Rescue Mission': 'A 2018 Sony VR platformer starring Astro Bot, designed as a flagship showcase for PlayStation VR.',
      'Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice': 'A 2019 FromSoftware action game set in Sengoku-era Japan, emphasizing precise parry-based sword combat.',
      'League of Legends': 'A 2009 Riot Games multiplayer online battle arena (MOBA) and one of the most-played esports titles in the world.',
      'Beat Saber': 'A VR rhythm game where players slash colored blocks to the beat of music using lightsaber-like controllers.',
      'The Last of Us Part II': 'A 2020 Naughty Dog narrative action game following Ellie in a post-apocalyptic world, exploring cycles of violence.',
      'Half-Life: Alyx': 'A 2020 Valve VR first-person shooter set between Half-Life and Half-Life 2, starring Alyx Vance.',
      'It Takes Two': 'A 2021 Hazelight co-op platformer following a couple working through their divorce via imaginative game mechanics.',
      'Resident Evil 4': 'The 2021 Oculus VR adaptation of Capcom\'s survival horror classic, rebuilt for virtual reality.',
      'Elden Ring': 'A 2022 FromSoftware open-world action RPG developed with George R.R. Martin, set in the shattered Lands Between.',
      'Valorant': 'A 2020 Riot Games tactical first-person shooter blending precise gunplay with hero abilities.',
      'Moss: Book II': 'A 2022 Polyarc VR puzzle-adventure game following mouse hero Quill through a storybook fantasy world.',
